title: How to Develop 7-Figure Social Skills, ft. Jordan Harbinger, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO237
itunes:title: How to Develop 7-Figure Social Skills, ft. Jordan Harbinger, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO237
description: In business & life, people who master the "soft skills" make an impact & make money. Jordan Harbinger is one of the pioneers of podcasting & is an expert in social dynamics. A guy who built a massively successful brand by providing high quality content & generating meaningful conversations on critical issues, Jordan joins me in the studio & we talk about the interpersonal dynamics that translate into big-time influence & income.
